data.description: Absolute amazing home. Everything State of the Art. Over 250K was spent on improvements and renovations. This home consists of 3 bedrooms with 3 1/2 baths. The first level features a large bedroom, spacious modern kitchen with all stainless steel appliances, granite counter-top and  granite floors, living and dining room, with a full-bath. The second level features one huge bedroom with a full-bath and Jacuzzi, along with a Master-bedroom and full-bath. Lovely balcony in front of second floor. Nicely done basement for indoor entertaining, laundry facilities and 1/2 bath. Nice yard for your enjoyment of the outdoors and  large concrete garage for storage and huge extension to the rear of the home. Split A/C units through-out the home and camera system. This home can be easily converted to a two family.  Close proximity to all amenities, schools, shops, buses, parks, restaurants and much more. Must see to appreciate.
